Final proposal
Topic: Social media pros and cons.

Abstract: Progression in technology lead to changes in society, this notion has been part of human history since the stone age. Today, we 
faced yet another change as the world wide web become part of our everyday lives. The internet exist to broaden communication around the 
world and also allows for quick information exchange, often in the form of social media. With the rise of social media, people are able to
share, advertise and explore from the comfort of their home. However, with great features come hefty consequences such as: the unrealistic
portrayal of  “living lavish” and body image causing self-esteem issues and depression. Moreover, social media also create a very hostile 
space as users pick on others for their look, wealth or style which can cause suicide and depression. 
 
 Essay presentation: Interactive video.
